- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with the language and structure of legal codes. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the implications of the network structure of legal codes on legal interpretation and research.
